How it appears in attention systems

Attention also has a hum, a compression phase, and a flip.

Attention Möbius Zero signs

* audience is vaguely interested but uncommitted
* multiple frames are possible
* no dominant interpretation exists yet
* the first clean framing could take over

The nudge

* a phrase
* an image
* a timing choice
* a title
* a single repeated symbol

The key is simplicity, because simple inputs bind faster near ambiguity.

